<span id="fn_386"></span>[76:7](sbe0529.htm#fr_389.md) K20 has 'Spend.'

<span id="fn_387"></span>[76:8](sbe0529.htm#fr_390.md) Called Tort in § 24.

<span id="fn_388"></span>[77:1](sbe0529.htm#fr_391.md) Miswritten Araz in
