<span id="fn_412"></span>[80:2](sbe0529.htm#fr_415.md) The Murghâb.

<span id="fn_413"></span>[80:3](sbe0529.htm#fr_416.md) Or, 'in Khûrâsân.'

<span id="fn_414"></span>[80:4](sbe0529.htm#fr_417.md) Bâmian, near which
the river of Balkh has its source.

<span id="fn_415"></span>[80:5](sbe0529.htm#fr_418.md) Justi observes that
